  11 Jul 2015; NP-Hardass <NP-Hardass@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml with mate herd

  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> mate-applets-1.8.0-r1.ebuild,
